results.title: Wolverine Origins (2006) #41
results.description: SEVEN THE HARD WAY PART 1 Any plan that Wolverine devises, Romulus anticipates. The solution? Use a plan that requires the participation of several different and very unlikely characters plucked from all corners of the Marvel Universe.

results.title: Wolverine Origins (2006) #42
results.description: SEVEN THE HARD WAY PART 2 Wolverine's extremely unconventional plan to take down Romulus takes yet another twist, as he now finds himself plotting a prison break. And who is it he's planning to spring? Would you believe...Ruby Thursday?!

results.title: Wolverine Origins (2006) #43
results.description: SEVEN THE HARD WAY PART 3 With Bruce Banner, Skaar, and Cloak on his side, Wolverine's mysterious plan to finally defeat Romulus seems to be going well...but that was before coming face to face with Kenuichio Harada, the Silver Samurai!
